Track individual attribute changes.

## Python Behavior

```python
@event.listens_for(User.email, 'set')
def on_email_change(target, value, oldvalue, initiator):
    if value != oldvalue:
        send_verification_email(target, value)
```

## Rust Implementation

```rust
#[derive(Model)]
struct User {
    #[sqlmodel(on_set = "on_email_change")]
    email: String,
}

impl User {
    fn on_email_change(&mut self, old: &str, new: &str) {
        if old != new {
            send_verification_email(self, new);
        }
    }
}
```

